# AI Context Configuration - scripts/

## Directory Purpose
Automation scripts for common operational tasks.

## AI Indexing Priority
PRIORITY: MEDIUM
Operational tools - index when working on automation or running tasks.

## Scope
AUTOMATION - Scripts for bootstrapping, validation, testing, and maintenance.

## Key Scripts
- bootstrap.ps1 - Initial setup
- test.ps1 - Run tests (CI-friendly)
- validate_workstreams.py - Workstream validation
- validate_workstreams_authoring.py - Authoring validation
- run_workstream.py - Execute workstreams
- generate_spec_index.py - Generate spec indices
- generate_spec_mapping.py - Generate spec mapping
- run_error_engine.py - Error pipeline execution

## Script Conventions
- Prefer PowerShell (.ps1) for Windows-first flows
- Provide .sh parity where feasible (no WSL-only assumptions)
- Python for cross-platform logic
- Keep scripts simple - complex logic belongs in modules

## When to Use This Section
- Adding automation scripts
- Maintaining existing scripts
- Understanding operational workflows
- Setting up development environment

## Related Sections
- core/ - Core functionality scripts interact with
- tests/ - Test infrastructure
- docs/ - Documentation on usage

## Exclude from Context
- __pycache__/
- *.pyc
- logs/
